00:08:57.537 --> 00:09:01.209 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: And as you said, we
talked about this in our last

00:09:01.209 --> 00:09:01.708 align:middle line:90%
interview.

00:09:01.708 --> 00:09:05.512 align:middle line:84%
Basically, this is a con game,
a confidence game right now.

00:09:05.512 --> 00:09:06.546 align:middle line:90%
>> Hoffman: Absolutely.

00:09:06.546 --> 00:09:08.882 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: The entire
economy is a con game.

00:09:08.882 --> 00:09:11.184 align:middle line:84%
>> Hoffman: And as the Ponzi
scheme is getting larger,

